<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="hire-v">hire <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'haɪə(r)/    美 /'haɪər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-bre-ame-rent">1.★ <strong>(BrE) (短期) 租用 (AmE rent)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>hire a car / boat 
租车/船</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>(临时) 雇用：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the power to hire and fire 
聘用和解雇的权力</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She hired some technical experts and started her own company in 2004.
2004年她聘请了一些技术专家，开办了自己的公司。</p><footer>2014 天津</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>hire sb to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ll hire a lawyer to handle the case.
我将聘请一位律师来处理这一案件。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="hire-out">hire out</h3>
<p>1.<strong>出租：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The company hires out cars.
这家公司出租小汽车。</p></div></div>